'''Grace''' runs the store [[Grace's Graceful Clothing]] in the [[Rogues' Den]] and exchanges [[Mark of grace|marks of grace]] earned by participating in [[rooftop agility course]]s for parts of the [[graceful clothing]] set which reduces [[weight]] as well as [[amylase pack]]s which contain 100 [[amylase crystal]]s, which are combined with [[super energy]] potions to create [[stamina potion]]s.

Grace keeps count of the number of completed laps of every rooftop or agility course in the game. Players may speak to Grace to toggle completed lap chatbox announcements, which does not disable tracking their count.

She owns a dog named [[Mark (dog)|Mark]].
[[File:Agility Course Lap Counts.png|alt=Grace's lap counter interface|thumb|Grace's lap counting interface.]]

