==Trivia==
*After the [[graceful outfit]]'s [[graphical update]] in [[Update:Boss Pets and Spawn Rates|an update]] on [[17 July]] [[2014]], Grace still wore the previous version of the outfit. This was an oversight, and was properly updated [[Update:F2P Trial Expansion & More|the next week]].
*Grace was named after [[Mod Mat K]]'s dog.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1312086741747150849|date=2 October 2020|archiveurl=https://archive.is/wip/Y0SDp|archivedate=8 March 2021|quote=No, the item descriptions were pretty specifically about one's graceful quality. I wrote them on purpose. Grace herself was named after Mod Mat K's dog, for what it's worth. That's why she was given a dog that resembles his dog.}}

